{
 "name": "RPlog_Sinister_Stranger",
 "title": "Sinister Stranger",
 "summary": "Enjoying a quiet evening in Plaxton City's Fountain Square, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios is approached by the dapper, sinister stranger Ash Seneal, who unsettlingly knows her name and presses an unopened tourist map into her hands while hinting that he wants 'something' from her before vanishing into the trees with a promise that he'll be seeing her. Shaken, Jessalyn meets her companion Orson Tighe, who arrives lugging a crate of equipment, and tells him of the unnerving encounter. They discover the stranger has marked their hotel on the map, and Orson -- whose crate holds tools to upgrade her board and secretly craft a lightsaber -- suggests they relocate to a place on the beach and keep watch for the man. Comforted, Jessalyn agrees, troubled to have been followed without sensing it.",
